reviewText: I found this at a brick & mortar store in the bargain bin, all 3 seasons for $4.95. I was not familiar with the show at all but the premise sounded promising. LOVE IT! Quirky characters, off the wall humor and hilarious situations. This is far superior to many of the poor comedies that currently populate the prime time commercial networks and/or cable. The entire cast is superb and gifted performers. I was sorry when I had finished watching all 21 episodes because I wanted more! This is a series I will watch more than once. Delightful!
All seasons! Great show - wish that there were more seasons !
wished the show went longer, glad to have found it on dvd
Hilarious!!  Funny, kind of goofy , sort of like The Office. WE like it a lot. Too bad tghere were only a few seasons.
sad to know this is it...very dry humor but super funny.
Funny and offbeat, a good way to dip your foot into the HowlerTV pool.  But you are gonna want more. HowlerTV.com
This show is so amazing- especially if you work retail.

A funny show based on the antics and interactions of the employees of a gracery store.  Having worked in one for over 11 years...I can't tell you how much of this art imitates life!  Very cute and recommended for some genuine laughs.  The product itself was complete, brand new and in perfect working order.
Fun, silly little show. Fast ship. Good price.
